  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.2">
<l>vāyōrī raiññūṟututaṅka ḷārnta</l>
<l>vaḷaiyuṭampi ṉaḻalnāka mumiḻnta centī</l>
<l>vīyāta malarcceṉṉi vitāṉa mēpōl</l>
<l>mēṉmēlu mikaveṅkum paranta taṉkīḻk</l>
<l>kāyāmpū malarppiṟaṅka laṉṉa mālaik</l>
<l>kaṭiyaraṅkat taravaṇaiyiṟ paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>māyōṉai maṇattūṇē paṟṟi niṉṟeṉ</l>
<l>vāyāra veṉṟukolō vāḻttu nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day that [I] will stand clutching the ‘Fragrance’ pillars [and]</l>
<l>praise to the satisfaction of my mouth</l>
<l rend="indent">Māl who resembles a mountain that blooms with ironwood flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">Māyōṉ  who sleeps on the serpent-bed in the [well-]defended  Raṅgam,</l>
<l rend="indent">[lying] beneath  [the fire]</l>
<l>as the red fire</l>
<l rend="indent">- which was spit [out] by the fiery serpent with a coiled  body,</l>
<l rend="indent">[its] unique thousand mouths  filled with verses of praise  -</l>
<l>spreads everywhere so that it increases higher and higher,</l>
<l>just like a canopy to [His] head that is [like] an unwithering  blossom.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
